{"tid":2186722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果日報文章支持Trump連任。黎智英助手：只代表作者個人立場。","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T08:40:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"590db68584da5cf3f1e387d1dc7e72ec257a5e99","tid":2186722,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報文章支持Donald Trump連任，被法新社記者質疑這是報紙官方立場，又直指壹傳媒高層跟Trump政府關係密切。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英助手Mark Simon澄清指文章只代表作者個人立場。但<strong>Mark Simon</strong>又指出Trump政府比Obama政府更支持香港，佢<strong>自己上年夏天和年尾都曾經去過美國白宮，可以做証。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzYKtaL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzYKtaL.png&h=11b0f468&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1301385470425718785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1301385470425718785&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=835f3c1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1301385470425718785&h=7913623d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1301385470425718785</a>"},{"pid":"ad7316c492c94ead63914fcb31184d3c30cdcb6c","tid":2186722,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"再提提：Mark Simon係共和黨人。"},{"pid":"491715e55605b121f40be667dc9a4c962996374e","tid":2186722,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:06:27.000Z","msg":"某d人仲成日屈黎智美親美國民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd5f24d21c2faaf8d5733a4c2e51c5e99c4e4fe","tid":2186722,"uid":283764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"不過蘋果新聞標題似幫民主黨多，可能想買兩邊。"},{"pid":"32824fcd9349e40642d012decdb51e96a37386ae","tid":2186722,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,